verbose_text: Since Msx1/2, Ngn2 and Nurr1 are expressed mostly in restricted non overlapping NPCs that are linked along the dopaminergic differentiation pathway, the mRNA levels determined are in agreement with a differentiation flux starting with a definite number of Msx1+ NPCs that are converted into dopaminergic neurons passing sequentially through Ngn2+ and Nurr1+ NPCs.
